@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cviwww(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.72)) - ((v2 + 0.17 * v1 + 0.15) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.15)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.99)) - v2)
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.78)) * 0.03)
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
